metrics.name: vcenter.host.cpu.usage
metrics.description: The amount of CPU used by the host.

metrics.name: vcenter.host.cpu.utilization
metrics.description: The CPU utilization of the host system.

metrics.name: vcenter.host.disk.latency.max
metrics.description: Highest latency value across all disks used by the host.

metrics.name: vcenter.host.disk.throughput
metrics.description: Average number of kilobytes read from or written to the disk each second.

metrics.name: vcenter.host.memory.usage
metrics.description: The amount of memory the host system is using.

metrics.name: vcenter.host.memory.utilization
metrics.description: The percentage of the host system's memory capacity that is being utilized.

metrics.name: vcenter.host.network.packet.count
metrics.description: The number of packets transmitted and received, as measured over the most recent 20s interval.

metrics.name: vcenter.host.network.throughput
metrics.description: The amount of data that was transmitted or received over the network by the host.

metrics.name: vcenter.host.network.usage
metrics.description: The sum of the data transmitted and received for all the NIC instances of the host.
